org.tron.common.utils

Class DataWord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tron.common.utils.DataWord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<DataWord>

    public class DataWord
extends Object
implements Comparable<DataWord>
    DataWord is the 32-byte array representation of a 256-bit number Calculations can be done on this word with other DataWords
    Since:
    01.06.2014
    Author:
    Roman Mandeleil

        public int intValue()
        Converts this DataWord to an int, checking for lost information. If this DataWord is out of the possible range for an int result then an ArithmeticException is thrown.
        Returns:
